Job Description
To provide Local Business Partners and customers with Engineering"technical application support for Fisher control valves product families. Assist and support technical people working on new and existing control valve industry applications.
Assist and support Technical people for any technical & commercial quires for Fisher products and services.
Assist and support Technical people with Fisher products system sizing and selection.
Reviewing customer specs and submit any comments & Deviations.
Define application solutions appropriate to customer requirements and be sure technical team quote fit for purpose solution.
Process and implement specifications for required specific control valve applications.
Job Requirements
Mechanical Engineering Degree
3+ years experience as an Application Engineer with valve related products